snippet.title: Egg Whisperer Show
snippet.description:
In 2016, Dr. Aimee Eyvazzadeh, started her weekly Egg Whisperer Show as a way of promoting fertility awareness. Met with her characteristic kindness and humor, Dr. Aimee’s focus on the Egg Whisperer Show is to provide information to her audience that they can not find anywhere else, and present it in a way that is accessible, and easy to understand.

Each week she takes to Facebook Live and YouTube from her studio to talk about topics that range from debunking fertility myths, to sharing about fertility procedures, and providing practical tips on giving oneself fertility shots. She also interviews expert guests who share about topics such as nutrition, acupuncture, men’s fertility, and sperm.

You can find the Egg Whisperer Show on:
Facebook Live: https://www.facebook.com/aimee.eyvazzadeh
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/eggwhisperershow
iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-egg-whisperer-show/id1253210160?mt=2
Google Podcasts: http://theeggwhisperer.libsyn.com/
